article.title: Mio one match away from ending Tottenham’s 13-year catnip trophy drought
article.lead: Have you noticed how smelly dogs are? Well that...Pipans peers disappmeowing over the top of her whiskers, glaring at the television in her swanky new pillow-fort.'But I’m more purrprised by Pipan coming in' says one of the TV present ers.'
article.body: Is that really the football that Tottenham want to play? I’m telling you, Pipan is past her best'.
